    "description": "《血脉传说》是一款开放世界奇幻动作RPG游戏，玩家将扮演先驱者血脉的后裔，相传该血脉拥有远古之神的预见神力，能够保护欧铎斯大陆免受“无赦者”的侵犯。这种传说似乎早已湮灭在历史的尘埃中……然而你却在自己的幻视中，看到了大举进犯的“无赦者”，看到了损失惨重的先驱者，看到了生灵涂炭的大地。<br><br><strong>以鲜血书写的传奇旅途。</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 自由决定如何进行冒险。推进任务主线并帮助欧铎斯大陆的人们，也可以按照自己的节奏在这片大陆上自由探索，去体验遭遇的随机事件。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/457c4341ee3b850493e7147e803bfa85.poster.avif?t=1758122352\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/457c4341ee3b850493e7147e803bfa85.webm?t=1758122352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/457c4341ee3b850493e7147e803bfa85.mp4?t=1758122352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> 在不同王国之间进行斡旋，建设属于自己的村庄，为击败死灰复燃的“无赦者”做好万全的准备。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/401458aca33a57f3ba71497065891e6d.poster.avif?t=1758122352\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/401458aca33a57f3ba71497065891e6d.webm?t=1758122352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/401458aca33a57f3ba71497065891e6d.mp4?t=1758122352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> 探索这片大地，加入各种公会，狩猎神奇生物，或是找家当地旅馆去当个吟游诗人——选择权都在自己手上，用自己喜欢的方式来体验这款游戏。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/be4d7da3609f8ce3b2ff95a2fe7e1693.poster.avif?t=1758122352\" width=600 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/be4d7da3609f8ce3b2ff95a2fe7e1693.webm?t=1758122352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/be4d7da3609f8ce3b2ff95a2fe7e1693.mp4?t=1758122352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> 自由游玩，获得奖励——能做出的每一个动作几乎都拥有等级系统。从跳跃、攀爬、奔跑到乱蹦、跑墙与游泳！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/c6514a3b907754e57f1e705b3bc9aecb.poster.avif?t=1758122352\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/c6514a3b907754e57f1e705b3bc9aecb.webm?t=1758122352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/c6514a3b907754e57f1e705b3bc9aecb.mp4?t=1758122352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> 制作工具和装备，捕捉稀有鱼类，烹饪稀奇古怪的菜肴，调制药水，甚至还能变身为猛兽……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/c86d9df877a588966a4368029b91cee7.poster.avif?t=1758122352\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/c86d9df877a588966a4368029b91cee7.webm?t=1758122352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/c86d9df877a588966a4368029b91cee7.mp4?t=1758122352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> 利用自己的预见神力（能够预见即将发生的事件）来规划冒险。能够预见陨石风暴、地精袭击，甚至还有幽灵海盗船！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/6be4b0e911298c4bee14e10c721ad1f2.poster.avif?t=1758122352\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/6be4b0e911298c4bee14e10c721ad1f2.webm?t=1758122352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/6be4b0e911298c4bee14e10c721ad1f2.mp4?t=1758122352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> 广阔的世界等待探索！这片大陆上生活着不同的生物群落以及各种独特的动植物，还充满了多样的地貌地标：繁华的城镇，宏伟的城堡，神秘的湖泊，危险的地牢等等。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/f17c6cf979cfbd325a32755308849258.poster.avif?t=1758122352\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/f17c6cf979cfbd325a32755308849258.webm?t=1758122352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/f17c6cf979cfbd325a32755308849258.mp4?t=1758122352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> 自定义游戏风格！可以解锁500种以上的技能，能够使用数百种不同的武器和装备，能够完全自定义自己的角色。可以成为一名蛰伏于暗影的沉默刺客，或是成为一位使用至圣斩的重甲圣武士。还可以选择一些更加独特有趣的搭配——一名使用武术的死灵法师，或是一位可以变身为动物的驭械德鲁伊。选择权完全在你。 </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/149f047dffecdd3e0fc348557e71150b.poster.avif?t=1758122352\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/149f047dffecdd3e0fc348557e71150b.webm?t=1758122352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1159290/extras/149f047dffecdd3e0fc348557e71150b.mp4?t=1758122352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
